Description: AI-powered 3D world generator for robotics
 Burma Automaton uses Microsoft's BitNet.cpp for efficient
 1.58-bit LLM inference to generate 3D simulation worlds
 from natural language descriptions.
 .
 Features include:
  * Natural language to 3D world conversion
  * Gazebo SDF export
  * RViz map conversion
  * Material and lighting management
